@{
	ViewBag.Title = "Privacy Policy";
}



<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
	<title>Privacy Policy</title>
	<style>
		/* Add some padding and a border around the main content area */
		.content {
			padding: 20px;
			border: 1px solid #ccc;
			border-radius: 5px;
			background-color: #fff;
			box-shadow: 0px 0px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
			/* Add animation to the content */
			animation-name: fadeIn;
			animation-duration: 1s;
			animation-fill-mode: forwards;
		}

		/* Add a background image to the page */
		body {
			background-color: black;
			background-color: rgba();
			background-blend-mode: saturation;
			background-size: cover;
		}

		/* Style the headings */
		h1, h2 {
			font-weight: bold;
			margin-top: 40px;
			margin-bottom: 20px;
			/* Add hover effects to the headings */
			transition: color 0.3s ease-in-out;
		}

			h1:hover, h2:hover {
				color: #007bff;
			}

		/* Style the unordered list */
		ul {
			list-style: disc;
			margin-left: 30px;
			margin-bottom: 20px;
			/* Add a subtle animation to the list */
			animation-name: slideInLeft;
			animation-duration: 1s;
			animation-fill-mode: forwards;
		}

		/* Style the paragraphs */
		p {
			margin-bottom: 20px;
			line-height: 1.5;
			/* Add a subtle animation to the paragraphs */
			animation-name: slideInRight;
			animation-duration: 1s;
			animation-fill-mode: forwards;
		}

		/* Style the contact link */
		a {
			color: #007bff;
			text-decoration: none;
			/* Add hover effects to the links */
			transition: color 0.3s ease-in-out;
		}

			a:hover {
				color: #007bff;
				text-decoration: underline;
			}
	</style>
</head>

<body>
	<div class="content">
		<h1>@ViewBag.Title</h1>

		<p>Thank you for visiting our website. Your privacy is important to us. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our website.</p>

		<h2>Information We Collect</h2>

		<p>We may collect the following information:</p>

		<ul>
			<li>Your name and contact information</li>
			<li>Your payment information, if you make a purchase on our website</li>
			<li>Information about your use of our website, such as your IP address, browser type, and pages you visit</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>

		<p>We use your information for the following purposes:</p>

		<ul>
			<li>To provide and improve our website and services</li>
			<li>To communicate with you about your account or our services</li>
			<li>To process your orders and payments</li>
			<li>To comply with legal and regulatory requirements</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>How We Protect Your Information</h2>

		<p>We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure.</p>

		<h2>Disclosure of Your Information</h2>

		<p>We may disclose your personal information to the following entities:</p>

		<ul>
			<li>Our third-party service providers who help us operate our website and provide our services</li>
			<li>Law enforcement or other government officials as required by law</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>Changes to Our Privacy Policy</h2>

		<p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page.</p>

		<p>If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy, please <a href="#">contact us</a>.</p>
	</div>
</body>
